OL,3,CDiver who found girl drowned at
OL,4,Cwaterpark says lake had 'almost zero
OL,5,Cvisibility'
OL,7,FThe diver who found an 11-year-old
OL,8,Fgirl who drowned at a waterpark said
OL,9,Fthe lake "had almost zero visibility",
OL,10,Fan inquest has heard.
OL,12,FKyra Hill got into difficulty in a
OL,13,Fdesignated swimming area at Liquid
OL,14,FLeisure near Windsor, Berkshire, in
OL,15,FAugust 2022.
OL,17,FA 17-year-old lifeguard dived in after
OL,18,Fher at 3.20pm before leaving the water
OL,19,Fto radio her colleagues.
