OL,7,FAt 3.44pm, around 13 minutes before
OL,8,Femergency services were called, the
OL,9,Fpark owner called an off-duty
OL,10,Ffirefighter who lived nearby and was a
OL,11,Fdivemaster, Berkshire Coroner's Court
OL,12,Fheard on Thursday (15 May).
OL,14,FChris Knight, who previously worked at
OL,15,Fthe park, picked up at around 4.19pm
OL,16,Fand CCTV showed Mr Knight first
OL,17,Fentering the water with an oxygen tank
OL,18,Fat 4.33pm.
OL,20,FHe found Kyra at around 5.10pm.
