OL,7,FThe diver said he searched two parts
OL,8,Fof the lake before he was told that
OL,9,FCCTV showed her going under at another
OL,10,Flocation.
OL,12,FHe said that as far as he was aware no-
OL,13,Fone had looked at the CCTV by the time
OL,14,Fhe arrived at the park.
OL,16,FMr Knight emerged from the water with
OL,17,FKyra about 12 minutes after he started
OL,18,Flooking in the third area.
