OL,7,FDescribing the final search, the
OL,8,Ffirefighter said: "Because everything
OL,9,Felse had seemed slow, that seemed
OL,10,Ffast".
OL,12,FMr Knight said no divers worked at the
OL,13,Fpark and and he helped staff there
OL,14,F"very occasionally".
OL,16,FAsked if he was the most convenient
OL,17,Fdiver for Liquid Leisure to call in
OL,18,Fresponse to emergency, he said: "I
OL,19,Fwould say I was the only option."
