OL,7,FFinding Kyra would be like looking for
OL,8,Fa "needle in a haystack" for a surface
OL,9,Fswimmer diving down, Mr Knight said.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's not impossible but they
OL,12,Fwould have been very lucky to have
OL,13,Fgone to the right spot, to have gone
OL,14,Fdown to that depth with almost zero
OL,15,Fvisibility."
OL,17,F"I could probably see a metre at most
OL,18,Fand that's like seeing a shadow in a
OL,19,Fmetre, rather than seeing in detail,"
OL,20,Fhe added.
