OL,7,FMr Knight had known Liquid Leisure
OL,8,Fowner and director Stuart Marston for
OL,9,Faround three decades.
OL,11,FHe said he started wakeboarding at
OL,12,FLiquid Leisure shortly after it opened
OL,13,Fand later worked there.
OL,15,FAfter moving careers, Mr Knight
OL,16,Fcontinued to work there part-time.
OL,18,FHe said he had never had any concerns
OL,19,Fabout safety at the park.
