OL,7,FAt the start of Thursday's hearing,
OL,8,Fsenior coroner Heidi Connor warned
OL,9,Fthat she is "not hesitant to up the
OL,10,Fpolice presence" for the inquest.
OL,12,FShe said people have a right to give
OL,13,Fevidence "without fears for their
OL,14,Fsafety" and did not specify what this
OL,15,Freferred to.
OL,17,FMrs Connor also reminded those giving
OL,18,Fevidence to "tell the truth".
