OL,7,FTwo Thames Valley officers arrived
OL,8,Fduring the close of the morning
OL,9,Fsitting.
OL,11,FThe coroner pointed them out and
OL,12,Fadded: "The reason why we stand and
OL,13,Fbow at inquests ` it is not for me, it
OL,14,Fis not for the court, it is out of
OL,15,Frespect for Kyra and I must insist
OL,16,Fthat these proceedings remain
OL,17,Frespectful to Kyra."
OL,19,FThe inquest continues.
